# react-chat-lite

An open-source chat component written with TypeScript, based on React and Tailwind CSS. This component provides a customizable and easy-to-integrate chat UI for your web applications.

## Table of Contents

- [react-chat-lite](#react-chat-lite)
  - [Table of Contents](#table-of-contents)
  - [Features](#features)
  - [Installation](#installation)

## Features

- Real-time chat interface
- Responsive design
- Built with TypeScript, React, and Tailwind CSS
- Highly customizable and easy to theme

## Installation

To install the chat component, run:

```bash
pnpm i react-chat-lite
```
